    <notes>
<![CDATA[
* removed endpoints code in favor of a xml definition and generic methods [izi];
* better validation of parameters [izi];
* update API changes and add the new API methods (update_account, update_background_image etc...) [izi];
* switch to JSON format as default (XML is still available) [izi]
* switch to HTTP_Request2 [izi];
* make the test suite runnable locally with mock HTTP responses and improved code coverage (near 100%) [izi]; 
* cosmetic CS changes (removed licence in source code, added vim folds etc...) [izi];
* fixed bugs #15072 #15084 #15085 #15358 and #15472 [izi].
]]>
